{"tid":236820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拍拖成本】約會一次使$865？香港拍拖使費亞洲第二貴","createTime":"2017-05-10T04:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T07:57:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4ab4d2beaf3ec48ea0edc007c8e5e4230eded2","tid":236820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jcKRkdUQrxQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjcKRkdUQrxQ&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=09c83f62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jcKRkdUQrxQ</a><br />\n發佈日期：2017年5月9日<br />\n【本報訊】德意志銀行最新公佈了全球物價指數，統計了47個城市的花費，其中一項以「廉價約會」為指標，包括的士費、兩份午餐或晚餐、飲品、兩張戲票和幾杯啤酒的價錢作統計。結果顯示，香港於「拍拖成本」最貴城市中排行第20位，拍一次拖二人須花費110.8美金（即約865港元），屬亞洲第二高消費城市，比去年上升6位。"},{"pid":"11251fac08cbcda054ce6c01341e753efae8c22b","tid":236820,"uid":112078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"我真係想知佢點計"},{"pid":"6347000fa91430e504a6005b6dadd55d6202586e","tid":236820,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"港女話要食放題兩位都唔只啦"},{"pid":"cfeff92adf8ef90b1327026fb0f36007f9c59409","tid":236820,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行過路過入黎睇下啦喂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼指大後又一垃圾學店</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n（各位DSE雞唔該入一入黎）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/7?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/7?ref=ios</a>"}]}